PowerHouse README
-----------------

Website: http://powerhouse.nullware.com

PowerHouse is an HTML/Javascript character planner for Champions Online™
players. It is similar to and inspired by championBuilder, written by Moritz
Hartmeier and maintained by Roxstar, which is a Java application that performs
a similar function.

